  seerName: The Enthroned Seer
  vigor: 11
  clarity: 8
  spirit: 16
  guard: 2
  traits:
  - 'They are a twisted heap of flesh, bone,

    and spikes of precious metal.'
  - 'Sees glimpses of the ultimate fate of

